1. **`task` tool** — single-agent dispatch, one prompt per call. Fanning out 345 calls sequentially in one turn is impractical.
2. **MCP `task` mcp tool** — would have to be one call per agent as well.
3. **`forge` agent for multi-agent** — same single-call constraint.

